px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wilco">Wilco</a>本周公布了他们自己的新字体的详细信息 - 请在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/soundtrack-of-my-life-wilco-jeff-tweedy-interview-3234625">我的生活原声带：威尔科的杰夫·特威迪</a></b></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-tweedy">Jeff Tweedy</a>和同事透露，新字体“Wilco Loft Sans”现已上市。该乐队由<a class="external-link" href="https://simplebits.com/about/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-offer-url="https://simplebits.com/about/" data-event-click="{&quot;element&quot;:&quot;ExternalLink&quot;,&quot;outgoingURL&quot;:&quot;https://simplebits.com/about/&quot;}" data-uri="4f3e6ebba5c0d4a0f1d539899414f518">SimpleBits</a>创建，在其<a class="external-link" href="https://wilcostore.com/collections/new-items/products/loft-sans-font" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-offer-url="https://wilcostore.com/collections/new-items/products/loft-sans-font" data-event-click="{&quot;element&quot;:&quot;ExternalLink&quot;,&quot;outgoingURL&quot;:&quot;https://wilcostore.com/collections/new-items/products/loft-sans-font&quot;}" data-uri="28f86b8109f988c2d2e7151d5f6a3544">商店</a>中将 Wilco Loft Sans 描述为“全大写、高对比度无衬线”。</p><p>他们还根据每个乐队成员演奏的乐器为他们分享了一个自定义图标。在乐队分享的社交媒体帖子中查看如下： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CzY_4cRsy-X/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div