ertines-live-1392x885.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Libertines-live-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">The Libertines</a>今天（11 月 10 日）宣布了 2024 年新的亲密俱乐部巡演的详细信息。查看以下所有日期。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-interview-pete-doherty-carl-barat-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-3517826">The Libertines 谈论干净和联系：“我们只是想在当下写出优美的歌曲”</a></strong></li></ul><p>上个月，该乐队宣布即将于 2024 年 3 月发行新专辑《All Quiet On The Eastern Esplanade》，其中收录<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/libertines-run-run-run-new-album-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-margate-tour-3514134">有单曲《Run Run Run》</a> 。</p><p>在阿尔比奥奈巡演中，乐队将于明年一月前往斯托克顿、利物浦、米尔顿凯恩斯、卡迪夫和德比巡演新专辑，然后下个月前往法尔茅斯、南安普顿、斯托克、利兹和格拉斯哥。</p><p>这些日期的门票将于周二（11 月 14 日）上午 10:30 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fthe-libertines-tickets%2Fartist%2F945319" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此</a>发售。歌迷还可以<a href="https://TheLibertines.lnk.to/AQOTEEPR" target="_blank" rel="noopener">从</a>乐队的官方商店预订他们即将推出的新专辑的手工编号限量版独家 CD 和演出门票。</p><p>谈到这次巡演，乐队表示，他们“很高兴能回到我们在这些汗流浃背的小俱乐部里的根源，在那里我们可以看到人群的眼白。”</p><h2> <strong>2024 年展会的日期为：</strong></h2><p><b>一月</b><br /><strong>23 - 斯托克顿，ARC</strong><br /> <strong>24 - 利物浦，洞穴俱乐部</strong><br /><strong>25 - 米尔顿凯恩斯，MK11</strong><br /> <strong>27 - 卡迪夫，Clwb 伊福·巴赫</strong><br /><strong>28 – 德比，毛茸茸的狗</strong></p><p><b>二月<br /></b><strong>11 - 法尔茅斯，公主馆<br /></strong><strong>12 – 南安普敦，机舱</strong><br /><strong>14 – 斯托克，地下</strong><br /><strong>15 - 利兹，衣柜</strong><br /><strong>16 - 格拉斯哥，奥兰莫尔</strong></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="浪荡子乐队在《东方滨海艺术中心一切安静》中谈论清洁和联系" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CtuPJQWz_mQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在专辑发行之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carl-barat">Carl Barat</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">Pete Doherty</a>向<em>NME</em>讲述了他们期待已久的第四张专辑的形成因素，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-interview-pete-doherty-carl-barat-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-3517826">清醒、团结感和“写出优美歌曲”的愿望</a>。观看上面的采访。</p><p>当被问及乐队是否还有他们想要实现的愿望清单时刻时，多尔蒂说：“我正在酝酿一批新的歌曲，我真的很想让卡尔听听并看看他能用它们做什么。 ”</p><p>巴拉特补充道：“我自己一直在努力创作完美的歌曲。我不知道你是否找到过。这有点西西弗斯式的，不是吗？我们会到达那里，或者不会。”</p><p>多尔蒂还谈到了他个人的清醒之旅是如何激励他出现在乐队中的， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-and-frederic-lo-drug-free-france-new-album-the-fantasy-life-of-poetry-and-crime-3143250">此前他曾分享过，在法国戒毒和过着平静的生活</a>帮助塑造了专辑《诗歌与犯罪的幻想生活》。合作者弗雷德里克·罗。</p><p> “这只是日常琐事，真的，”多尔蒂说。 “这是与恶魔的正面交锋，但因为我非常相信卡尔、加里、约翰和这张唱片，所以我很高兴。我只是想尽自己的一份力量，尽可能专业，让人们听到这些歌曲，然后去演奏它们。如果没有，我们可能会再试一次，或者只是继续与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-hotel-albion-rooms-margate-carl-barat-video-tour-interview-2770049">酒店</a>合作，看看我们是否可以对此做些什么。”</p><p>在聊天的其他地方，浪荡子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-tried-to-sit-down-and-write-some-screenplays-for-a-biopic-3520538">谈到了拍摄传记片的可能性</a>，并表示他们已经“尝试坐下来写一些剧本”。然而，多尔蒂表示，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pete-doherty-on-new-documentary-about-his-life-i-dont-think-ill-be-able-to-watch-it-again-3523960">不太可能再次观看即将上映的有关他生活的纪录片</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em>在回顾最近的纪录片<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/pete-doherty-stranger-in-my-own-skin-review-3531791">《彼得·多尔蒂：我自己的陌生人</a></em>》时表示：“德维达斯的电影可能很难观看，但它除了提醒人们毒瘾的可怕之外，至少它给了我们很多值得感激的东西也是为了。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-announce-intimate-uk-club-tour-for-2024-buy-tickets-3535891">The Libertines 宣布 2024 年亲密英国俱乐部巡演的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
罗伯特·德尼罗虐待老板案审判得出结论https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-de-niro-abuse-trial-3535922?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=robert-de-niro-abuse-TrialAlex Berry Fri, 10 Nov 2023 10:06:51 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3535922 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗伯特·德尼罗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该审判在纽约市进行，已持续两周</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-de-niro-abuse-trial-3535922">罗伯特·德尼罗（Robert De Niro）虐待老板的审判达成判决</a>后，首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上发表。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="罗伯特·德尼罗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-10_11-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robert-de-niro">罗伯特·德尼罗</a>的前私人助理对他提起的<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/film/robert-de-niro-assistant-lawsuit-abuse-3528587">诉讼</a>已经做出判决。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/killers-of-the-flower-moon-review-martin-scorsese-3448518">《花月杀手》评论：马丁·斯科塞斯令人心碎的真实犯罪冷门</a></li></ul><p>德尼罗的公司 Canal Productions 在被发现存在性别歧视后，被责令向德尼罗的长期私人助理格雷厄姆·蔡斯·罗宾逊支付超过 120 万美元。</p><p>然而，德尼罗本人被发现对虐待行为不承担个人责任。在此之前，德尼罗在纽约市进行了为期两周的审判，否认了所有关于他是虐待雇主的指控。 </p><figure id="attachment_3535928" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3535928" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3535928" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court.jpg" alt="罗伯特·德尼罗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Robert-De-Niro-leaving-court-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3535928" class="wp-caption-text">罗伯特·德尼罗于 2023 年 11 月 8 日在纽约市。图片来源：Getty/摄影：ADAM GREY/法新社，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> 41 岁的罗宾逊<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/robert-de-niro-claims-abuse-3527092">因与德尼罗当时的女友蒂芙尼·陈 (Tiffany Chen) 意见不合而于 2019 年辞去工作，随后对德尼罗提出了索赔</a>。她起诉德尼罗，索赔 1200 万美元，声称德尼罗名誉受损和严重精神困扰。</p><p>罗宾逊声称，2009年至2019年间，她被辱骂，被迫执行有辱人格的任务，并且在<em>《花月杀手》</em>明星拒绝给她写推荐信后，她很难找到另一份工作。</p><p>据<a href="https://news.sky.com/story/amp/robert-de-niros-company-ordered-to-pay-1-2m-in-gender-discrimination-lawsuit-but-star-not-personally-liable-13004477" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>天空新闻</em></a>报道，80 岁的德尼罗作证时告诉陪审员，他将罗宾逊的年薪增加了两倍，达到 30 万美元，提升了她的头衔，并说她利用了自己的财务优势，据报道从他那里窃取了约 85,000 美元的飞行里程。</p><p>虽然这位明星否认对他的助理大喊大叫，并认为她的说法是“无稽之谈”，但他承认自己斥责了她，并承认他“本可以”称她为“臭小子”，但坚称自己<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/film/robert-de-niro-assistant-lawsuit-abuse-3528587">“从来没有辱骂过”</a> 。</p><p>德尼罗的律师起诉罗宾逊违反忠诚和信托义务，随后于 2019 年对他提起诉讼，要求赔偿 600 万美元，其中包括返还 500 万飞行里程。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/11/09/arts/robert-de-niro-trial-gender-discrimination.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》报道</em></a>，经过五个小时的审议，由七人组成的陪审团一致决定，罗宾逊对 Canal 对她提出的索赔不承担责任。</p><p>然而，在周三的结案陈词中，德尼罗的律师理查德·舍恩斯坦似乎放弃了这个想法，称这些物品价值约 85,000 美元，虽然陪审员可以命令罗宾逊退还部分工资，但“我们并不是要你惩罚”她。”</p><p>罗宾逊的律师布伦特·汉纳凡（Brent Hannafan）在称过去两周为民权审判后，敦促陪审员“不仅为罗宾逊女士，而且为所有民权诉讼当事人”作出裁决。</p><p>据<a href="https://people.com/robert-de-niro-gender-discrimination-civil-case-trial-verdict-8387268" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《人物》杂志报道</em></a>，罗宾逊法律团队成员大卫·桑福德表示：“我们很高兴陪审团看到了我们所看到的情况，并做出了对蔡斯·罗宾逊有利、对罗伯特·德尼罗的公司 Canal Productions 有利的判决。”</p><p>他补充道，“罗宾逊女士不仅赢得了对卡纳尔的诉讼，而且陪审团认为德尼罗对她的指控毫无根据，完全证明了罗宾逊女士的清白。”<br />德尼罗的团队尚未发表评论。</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/robert-de-niro-abuse-trial-3535922">罗伯特·德尼罗（Robert De Niro）虐待老板的审判达成判决</a>后，首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上发表。</p> ;
安德烈亚·波切利 (Andrea Bocelli) 宣布担任 BST 海德公园 2024 年首个头条表演https://www.nme.com/news/music/andrea-bocelli-announced-first-headline-act-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3535927?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=andrea-bocelli-宣布第一条新闻法案 bst-海德公园-2024-购买门票Liberty DunworthFri, 10 Nov 2023 10:00:04 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNewsBST Hyde ParkLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3535927 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安德烈亚·波切利，2023" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>此次预订使他成为首位登上该音乐节头条的古典艺术家</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andrea-bocelli-announced-first-headline-act-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3535927">安德里亚·波切利 (Andrea Bocelli) 宣布成为 BST 海德公园 2024 年首个头条新闻的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="安德烈亚·波切利，2023" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Andrea-Bocelli@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>安德烈亚·波切利 (Andrea Bocelli) 已被确认为第一位出现在 2024 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST 海德公园</a>音乐节上的头条人物。</p><p>今天（11 月 10 日）宣布，这位著名古典歌手将在 7 月 5 日星期五的伦敦音乐节上担任主角，并且是唯一一位尚未宣布参加明年音乐节的艺术家。</p><p>即将到来的演出不仅是波切利计划在 2024 年在英国演出的唯一一场演出，而且也标志着现场音乐系列本身的一个里程碑，因为此次预订标志着 BST 海德公园首次成为头条新闻由一位古典音乐家创作。</p><p> 2024 年，这位曾售出 9000 万张唱片并为教皇、总统和皇室成员表演的艺术家还将庆祝其职业生涯 30 周年。</p><p> “I am delighted to see how today this anniversary has become a celebration for many: a collective way to celebrate three decades of music and excitement, of memories and feelings, that can bloom to life to the notes of a score each time,” Bocelli said of the upcoming celebration.</p><p> “Hyde Park is the perfect place for coming together to celebrate my 30th anniversary and reimagine it as a springboard propelling us into the future, imbued with positivity and the power of good. </p><figure id="attachment_3535933" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3535933" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3535933" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli.jpeg" alt="BST Hyde Park 2024, Andrea Bocelli artwork" width="2000" height="2829" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli.jpeg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli-400x566.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli-800x1132.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli-696x984.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli-1392x1969.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/BST-hyde-park-Bocelli-1068x1511.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3535933" class="wp-caption-text"> BST Hyde Park 2024, Andrea Bocelli artwork. CREDIT: Press</figcaption></figure><p> “Celebrating it here is sure to be unforgettable, in the vast green lung from which London has been drawing breath for hundreds of years, in this park that is the embodiment of a glorious chapter in the history of a nation, of a continent, of a civilisation… and also of so much wonderful music that has rung out here, nourishing it in its wake.”</p><div><p> Jim King, CEO of European Festivals at AEG Presents, added: “We have wanted to host Andrea Bocelli in Hyde Park for many years and so it&#39;s a great honour for us that we are able to share this special moment with him and his loyal fans. There can be no bigger occasion for all music than experiencing the world&#39;s greatest tenor in London&#39;s Hyde Park.”</p></div><p> Tickets for the BST Hyde Park show headlined by Bocelli go on sale next Wednesday (November 15) at 10am GMT. You can purchase them <a href="https://www.bst-hydepark.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> . </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Andrea Bocelli is headlining American Express presents BST Hyde Park" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/S74WAdOwbuE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Headliners for who appeared at BST Hyde Park this year included <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> , <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">P!nk</a> , <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/take-that">Take That</a> , <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-joel">Billy Joel</a> , <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen-and-the-e-street-band">Bruce Springsteen and The E Street Band,</a> <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a> and <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a> .</p><p> The news of the classical singer coming to BST arrives after it was confirmed that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andrea-bocelli-sings-in-italian-for-john-lewis-2023-christmas-advert-watch-3534782">he is the latest artist to star in the annual Christmas advert for John Lewis</a> .</p><p> Sung in Italian, his track &#39;Festa&#39; was written and produced by Italian duo Le Feste Antonacci specifically for the ad, and had its lyrics written for and approved by the renowned classical singer.</p><p> As well as featuring on the ad – which has become an annual staple over the holidays – the track is also released as a special deluxe version of his album &#39;A Family Christmas&#39;.</p><p> 10p from every track download will be donated to charity by Decca between the period of November 9 2023 and April 30 2024. The proceeds will be split between Action for Children and Home-Start UK – you can find out more about the charities <a href="https://www.actionforchildren.org.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> and <a href="https://www.home-start.org.uk/?gclid=Cj0KCQiAo7KqBhDhARIsAKhZ4uglV_YlAMYFqUUNbVj4XBCw6DdlEbQw6PYsyoegOxfYF8h5dHkC604aAnduEALw_wcB" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andrea-bocelli-announced-first-headline-act-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3535927">Andrea Bocelli announced as first headline act for BST Hyde Park 2024</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
